# Document workflow

## Ownership

| Content | Home | This repo keeps |
|---------|------|-----------------|
| Cross-repo ADR/ARC | [devdocs](../devdocs/) | contract-specific arc/adr |
| Platform ops | devdocs/ops | — |
| Domain glossary | [devdocs/glossary.md](../devdocs/glossary.md) | — |
| Contract plans/ADRs | `docs/{plans,adr,arc}/` | full doc |

## Layout

- `docs/arc/arc-NNNN-*.md`
- `docs/adr/adr-NNNN-*.md`
- `docs/plans/plan-NNNN-*.md`
- `docs/history/plans/` — superseded plans

## Numbering

Sequential NNNN per type under `docs/**`.

## Cross-referencing

Reference related documents in markdown. Platform docs in
[devdocs](../devdocs/) — see [docs/plans/README.md](../docs/plans/README.md).
